'''威廉·艾許利·弗里罕'''（{{lang-en|William Ashley Freehan}}，{{bd|1941年|11月29日|2021年|8月19日|catIdx=Freehan}}），<ref name="Bill Freehan at Baseball Reference">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/f/freehbi01.shtml?redir|title=Bill Freehan Stats - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205033201/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/f/freehbi01.shtml?redir|dead-url=no}}</ref>為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的捕手。職業生涯皆效力於[[底特律老虎|底特律老虎]]。他生涯入選11次明星賽，並在1968年拿下世界大賽冠軍與MVP第二名。

弗里罕生涯拿過5座金手套獎，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1966|title=MLB American League Gold Glove Award Winners - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329233506/https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/gold_glove_al.shtml#1966|dead-url=no}}</ref>守備率高達9成93。另外他職業生涯敲出200轟與2502個壘打數，在美聯捕手歷史上排名第三，僅次於兩位洋基傳奇名捕[[尤吉·貝拉|尤吉·貝拉]]和[[比爾·狄奇|比爾·狄奇]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://members.tripod.com/bb_catchers/catchers/fieldcar.htm|title=Encyclopedia of Baseball Catchers - Career Fielding Leaders|website=members.tripod.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926031309/http://members.tripod.com/bb_catchers/catchers/fieldcar.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==職業生涯==
弗里罕就讀於密西根大學。1961年，還是大學生的他曾繳出5成85的打擊率。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1010445/index.htm|title=Sports Illustrated, July 27, 1997|publisher=|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025121519/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/vault/article/magazine/MAG1010445/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>這使得老虎隊看上了他的天賦，同年便與他簽下了合約。該年他升上大聯盟，不過僅出賽4場比賽便回到小聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8SsDAAAAMBAJ&q=Bill+Freehan+baseball+digest&pg=PA58|title=''Bill Freehan: A Key Member of the 1968 Champion Tigers'', by Jim Sargent, Baseball Digest, Jun 2000, Vol. 59, No. 6, ISSN 0005-609X|publisher=}}</ref>1963年，弗里罕重返大聯盟。他原與Gus Triandos分擔捕手工作，不過隨著Triandos季中被交易，弗里罕也成為了老虎隊的主力捕手。

1964年，弗里罕繳出3成的打擊率，並敲出18轟與80分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1964-batting-leaders.shtml|title=1964 American League Batting Leaders - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106143836/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1964-batting-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他首度入選明星賽，並在MVP票選上拿下第七名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1964.shtml#ALmvp|title=1964 Awards Voting - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2009-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090330112104/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1964.shtml#ALmvp|dead-url=no}}</ref>1965年，弗里罕成為大聯盟接殺數最多的球員，他也因此拿下金手套獎。隔年他的接殺數和守備率一樣排在美聯第一。

1967年，弗里罕打出了生涯年。該年他的打擊率為2成82並敲出20轟。他在1021個守備機會拿下950次接殺為大聯盟最多。另外，他在故意四壞和觸身球次數上也都是聯盟第一。最後他在MVP票選上拿下第三名，不過老虎以1場勝差輸給紅襪無緣進軍世界大賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1967-batting-leaders.shtml|title=1967 American League Batting Leaders - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307222604/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1967-batting-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1967.shtml#ALmvp|title=1967 Awards Voting - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2010-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212112836/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1967.shtml#ALmvp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[File:Bill_Freehan_1966.jpg|thumb]]
1968年，這年號稱是大聯盟的投手大年，許多球員在這年的打擊數據都下滑不少。不過弗里罕仍敲出25轟與84分打點。<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1968.shtml|title=1968 American League Season Summary - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007234345/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1968.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他的接捕功力也很出色，儘管老虎主場是一座不利於投手的球場，但是弗里罕靠著他優異的配球能力，仍將團隊投手群的防禦率壓至2.71。<ref name="#1"/>這年老虎隊靠著Denny McLain拿下31勝以及[[米奇·羅里奇|米奇·羅里奇]]拿下17勝闖進世界大賽。1968年世界大賽第5戰，當時紅雀3比2領先。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET196810070.shtml|title=1968 World Series Game 5, St. Louis Cardinals at Detroit Tigers, October 7, 1968 - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011007/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET196810070.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過弗里罕在5局上抓到嘗試盜三壘的快腿[[盧·布羅克|盧·布羅克]]，最後老虎隊在7局下拿下3分逆轉。之後也一路得到勝利拿下冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1968_WS.shtml|title=1968 World Series - Detroit Tigers over St. Louis Cardinals (4-3) - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2007-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071129221726/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1968_WS.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他在MVP票選上拿下第二名，僅次於隊友McLain。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1968.shtml#ALmvp|title=1968 Awards Voting - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2009-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090330112109/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1968.shtml#ALmvp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1970年，儘管弗里罕的打擊能力出現下滑，不過他仍有47%的阻殺率和9成97的守備率。隔年他的打擊率為2成77，並敲出21轟。1972年，他的打擊率為2成62，球隊也拿下美聯東區冠軍。不過他因為拇指受傷而缺席了前兩場美聯冠軍賽。雖然老虎隊努力追回2場比賽，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210100.shtml|title=1972 American League Championship Series (ALCS) Game 3, Oakland Athletics at Detroit Tigers, October 10, 1972 - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309010748/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210100.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210110.shtml|title=1972 American League Championship Series (ALCS) Game 4, Oakland Athletics at Detroit Tigers, October 11, 1972 - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2018-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904154033/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210110.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>而且弗里罕也在第5場打回打點，不過老虎仍以1分惜敗給運動家。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210120.shtml|title=1972 American League Championship Series (ALCS) Game 5, Oakland Athletics at Detroit Tigers, October 12, 1972 - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218090352/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/DET/DET197210120.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>1974年，弗里罕轉任一壘手，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1974-batting-leaders.shtml|title=1974 American League Batting Leaders - Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-10-30|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308050105/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/AL/1974-batting-leaders.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔年又重回捕手這個老本行。1976年，他的打擊率為2成70，最後他在球季結束後退休。
