==個人生活==
弗里罕於1963年與妻子Pat結婚。<ref name=hospice>{{cite web|url=https://www.freep.com/story/sports/columnists/jeff-seidel/2018/10/28/bill-freehan-dementia-wife-detroit-tigers/1739616002/|title=As Bill Freehan lies in hospice care, his wife reveals their love story|publisher=Detroit Free Press|accessdate=2019-02-10|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102055819/https://www.freep.com/story/sports/columnists/jeff-seidel/2018/10/28/bill-freehan-dementia-wife-detroit-tigers/1739616002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他晚年深受阿茲海默症所苦，2018年10月，他在密西根州北部的安寧病房接受照顧。<ref name=hospice/>弗里罕后来于2021年8月19日逝世，享年79岁。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bill Freehan, catcher for 1968 World Series champion Tigers, dies at 79|url=https://www.detroitnews.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2021/08/19/bill-freehan-catcher-1968-champion-detroit-tigers-dies-79/8192888002/|first=Lynn|last=Henning|date=2021-08-19|access-date=2021-08-19|newspaper=The Detroit News|archive-date=2021-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210819225355/https://www.detroitnews.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2021/08/19/bill-freehan-catcher-1968-champion-detroit-tigers-dies-79/8192888002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

